8 Women;;76;;79;;R;;At an isolated mansion in the snowy countryside of 1950s France, a family is gathered for the holiday season. But there will be no celebration -- their beloved patriarch has been murdered! The killer can only be one of the eight women closest to the man of the house. Comedic situations arise with the revelations of dark family secrets. Eight women. Each is a suspect. One of them is guilty. Which one is it?;;Drama,Crime,Comedy,Musical;;François Ozon;;2002;;Catherine Deneuve,Isabelle Huppert,Emmanuelle Béart,Fanny Ardant,Virginie Ledoyen,Danielle Darrieux,Ludivine Sagnier,Firmine Richard;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/8_women